Distinctive Homes Dome is an indoor sporting arena located in Adelaide , Australia . It is the home arena of the Adelaide 36ers basketball team . The capacity of the arena is 7,200 , which includes courtside boxes , standard seating and elevated corporate suites . It now includes a number of food shops , bars . The Apollo Restaurant is used for pre - game dining and post - game interviews , and it also includes staff offices and player / coach facilities . The ' Dome was recently purchased by Eddy Groves ( ABC Learning CEO and Brisbane Bullets team owner ) . The naming rights sponsorship has now finished and is unlikely to be named Distinctive Homes Dome again . You can help by expanding it . 